/-!
# PARI/GP coefficients for `ineq2_trunc_leOne`

This file records the coefficient list (as rationals) for the truncation polynomial used in the
`t ≤ 1` case of Appendix A, Lemma `ineq2`. The list is extracted from the PARI/GP computations in
`appendix.txt` and is used in `SpherePacking.Dim24.Inequalities.Ineq2.LeOne.Trunc` for the
Sturm-style sign check.

## Main definitions
* `ineq2_trunc_leOne_coeffs_pari`
-/


